    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――kanaの誕生日数日前",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1933.3333333,
          "startTime": 1.9333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4540,
          "startTime": 4.54
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "四月十日はkanaの誕生日。みんなちゃーんとバズる\n物を寄越すこと。いいわね？　忘れたら許さないから",
      "startTime": 6.9706304785,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "（うーん……バズる物……釣り竿は怒られるかな？）\n（はっ！？　でも、バズる釣り竿なら……アリ？）",
      "startTime": 19.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――四月十日　早朝",
      "startTime": 24.8607938211,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2172.5395122,
          "startTime": 27.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ……おはようございまーす……誕生日の朝っぱら\nから仕事入れんなよ、クソポンコツマネージャー……",
      "startTime": 34.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3633.333659200005,
          "startTime": 37.9000003259
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさん！　誕生日おめでとうございます！\n……へへっ……一番にお祝い出来た……！",
      "startTime": 41.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとー。てか{user}は？　早朝から\n呼んどいて自分はまだ来てないとかありえないんだけど",
      "startTime": 48.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "あの……実は、{user}さんは来ません！\nkanaさんは今から私と二人で海に行きます！",
      "startTime": 56.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "は！？　海とか聞いてないんだけど！　それに\nマネージャーが同行しないってどういうことよ！？",
      "startTime": 64.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんにはkanaさんにサプライズ\nするため呼び出してもらっただけ……です",
      "startTime": 69.6000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "てことは……朝の情報番組のスタジオゲストの仕事は\n嘘だったってこと？　よくも人の睡眠時間を奪って――",
      "startTime": 78.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、朝の情報番組のスタジオゲストは嘘……\nでも、今から海にロケに行く！　これは本当の仕事！",
      "startTime": 88.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "海になんて行きたくないわよ！\nどーせ、あんたと釣りさせられるんでしょ！",
      "startTime": 95.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5900.0000000000055,
          "startTime": 101.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "ば、バレてる！　とりあえずこれ、私からの誕生日\nプレゼントです……！　開けてみて下さい！",
      "startTime": 103.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "開けなくても分かるわ！　この細長い棒みたいな形状で\n釣り竿じゃないことなんてある！？　ねーよなぁ？",
      "startTime": 110.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "ば、バレてる……うう……\nせっかくのサプライズが……でも……むんっ！",
      "startTime": 116.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、釣りロケなんて行かないから\nkanaは家帰って寝まーす。じゃあね～",
      "startTime": 125.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "待って……！　kanaさん、誕生日プレゼントには\nSNSでバズる物が欲しいって言った。だから私が……",
      "startTime": 132.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "必ずこの釣り竿でkanaさんに幻の珍魚を釣らせて\nバズらせます！　だから私と釣りに行って下さい！",
      "startTime": 141.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "幻の珍魚って……まあ、雫がここまで言うなら……うん\n分かった。でも、絶対にkanaのことバズらせろよ？",
      "startTime": 154.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』では私のお願い事\n沢山叶えてくれたからkanaさんのために頑張る！",
      "startTime": 164.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9066.6666667,
          "startTime": 173.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "あら？　SNSのトレンドにkanaさんの記事が……\n「kana、誕生日に巨大珍魚を一本釣り」",
      "startTime": 177.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんの誕生日、今日でしたのね！？\nヤバいですわ。プレゼントを用意しなくては……",
      "startTime": 187.1585290989,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}